{"tid":1733733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"poly人 我有一個大膽的想法","createTime":"2019-11-18T07:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T09:18:22.000Z","uid":170142,"like":85,"dislike":410,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc79aafdb5cda57f5092e6cc8151c334f8ff653","tid":1733733,"uid":170142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"燒咗個拉把佢，用盡你地所有嘅資源去燃燒拉把任何可以著火嘅野，成個poly最易燒又最難救嘅地方就係拉把<br />\n<br />\n要短時間內將火警升級至5級，要火警變成地區性災難，迫消防出大量車輛救援<br />\n<br />\nrisk好大，損失會好慘重，有手足會可能犧牲，需要堅定意志實行，但係你地唯一自救嘅機會，唔好再妄想外面嘅人會救到你地<br />\n<br />\n成功，可以全盤打亂癲狗部署，入面嘅人有fighting chance突出防線範圍<br />\n<br />\n照顧好身邊嘅人，唔好幻想會100%走得甩"},{"pid":"7cb30eec997fc89d4f727d4d87dbe8b0942ce590","tid":1733733,"uid":151324,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"消防唔救咪pk"},{"pid":"0cd36c0298d8a3fcfb23711c09d7943ea8f68515","tid":1733733,"uid":170142,"like":15,"dislike":27,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"以下預測child登仔回覆<br />\n包括 <br />\nno sir<br />\nmorning sir<br />\n拉<br />\n樓主係鬼<br />\n五毛想人燒圖書館"},{"pid":"5a8b0bc94708205c173e42c58f77d2b030a26432","tid":1733733,"uid":170142,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"7cb30eec997fc89d4f727d4d87dbe8b0942ce590","tid":1733733,"uid":151324,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"消防唔救咪pk"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"無得佢唔救"},{"pid":"6d8ab17ff074291f0e3d6764db93bf10afe84366","tid":1733733,"uid":218652,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"消防出動又點，都係走唔到"},{"pid":"b22568de9e6ee050d94673d92b0b222d16a48c63","tid":1733733,"uid":49699,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"ON9, 佢出面擺哂狗, 消防入去救完人, 出到黎就拉"},{"pid":"1195281d1dcc7819e1249d3248897b245e64d591","tid":1733733,"uid":49699,"like":109,"dislike":4,"score":105,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"你